impression_count.name: impression_count

like_count.name: like_count

ugc_post_urn.comment: The URN of the post record.

article_description.name: article_description
article_description.comment: Custom or saved description of the article. If empty, there is none.

article_source.name: article_source
article_source.comment: A URL of the article. Typically the URL that was ingested to maintain URL parameters.

article_thumbnail.name: article_thumbnail
article_thumbnail.comment: Custom or saved thumbnail for the article. If empty, there is none.

article_thumbnail_alt_text.name: article_thumbnail_alt_text
article_thumbnail_alt_text.comment: Alt text for the custom thumbnail. If empty, there is none.

article_title.name: article_title
article_title.comment: Custom or saved title of the article.

carousel_id.name: carousel_id
carousel_id.comment: The URN of the carousel content.

media_alt_text.name: media_alt_text
media_alt_text.comment: The alternative text for the media. None if empty.

media_title.name: media_title
media_title.comment: The title for media. None if empty.

multi_image_alt_text.name: multi_image_alt_text
multi_image_alt_text.comment: The alternate text of this thumbnail. Used for screen reader accessibility.

poll_question.name: poll_question
poll_question.comment: Question for the poll. Max length of 140 characters.

poll_settings_duration.name: poll_settings_duration
poll_settings_duration.comment: Duration of poll being open for votes.

poll_settings_is_voter_visible_to_author.name: poll_settings_is_voter_visible_to_author
poll_settings_is_voter_visible_to_author.comment: Poll author’s visibility to voters. Defaults to true.

poll_settings_vote_selection_type.name: poll_settings_vote_selection_type
poll_settings_vote_selection_type.comment: The selection type of votes on the poll. Defaults to SINGLE_VOTE.

poll_unique_voters_count.name: poll_unique_voters_count
poll_unique_voters_count.comment: Number of unique voters on the poll. Defaults to 0.

source_relation.name: source_relation
source_relation.comment: The source of the record, if the unioning functionality is being used.

organization_entity_urn.comment: The organizational entity URN for which the statistics represents.

share_entity_urn.name: share_entity_urn
share_entity_urn.comment: The share URN for describing individual share statistics. Is blank for aggregate share statistics.

engagement.name: engagement
engagement.comment: Number of organic clicks, likes, comments, and shares over impressions.

like_count.name: like_count
like_count.comment: Number of likes. This field can become negative when members who liked a sponsored share later unlike it. The like is not counted since it is not organic, but the unlike is counted as organic.
